
MegaBlock2 is shareware, and may be copied and freely distributed,
as long as all files on this disk remain intact and are not
altered in any way.

MegaBlock2 may be copied to a hard disk, simply by copying all files in
the archive to your hard disk.

The souce code for MegaBlock2 is compatible with both AMOSv1.3x and
Amos Professional v1.0 - v2.0

